parameters.query:
SELECT 
    c.id AS client_id,
    c.full_name,
    c.email,
    f.file_year,

    ff_overpay.field_value AS overpayment_amount,
    ff_estpay.field_value AS estimated_payments,

    ff_agi.field_value AS adjusted_gross_income,
    ff_tax.field_value AS total_tax_liability,

    ff_withheld_total.field_value AS total_withheld_taxes,
    ff_withheld_1099.field_value AS withheld_tax_from_1099,
    ff_withheld_w2.field_value AS withheld_tax_from_W2,
    ff_withheld_other.field_value AS withheld_tax_from_other_forms,

    ff_self_employment.field_value AS self_employment_tax

FROM clients c
JOIN files f ON f.client_id = c.id
JOIN forms fo ON fo.file_id = f.id

-- Join for overpayment
JOIN form_categories fc_overpay ON fc_overpay.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_overpay ON ff_overpay.category_id = fc_overpay.id
    AND ff_overpay.field_name = 'overpayment_amount'

-- Join for estimated payments
JOIN form_categories fc_estpay ON fc_estpay.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_estpay ON ff_estpay.category_id = fc_estpay.id
    AND ff_estpay.field_name = 'estimated_payments'

-- Join for adjusted gross income
JOIN form_categories fc_agi ON fc_agi.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_agi ON ff_agi.category_id = fc_agi.id
    AND ff_agi.field_name = 'adjusted_gross_income'

-- Join for total tax liability
JOIN form_categories fc_tax ON fc_tax.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_tax ON ff_tax.category_id = fc_tax.id
    AND ff_tax.field_name = 'total_tax'

-- Join for total withholdings
JOIN form_categories fc_withheld_total ON fc_withheld_total.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_withheld_total ON ff_withheld_total.category_id = fc_withheld_total.id
    AND ff_withheld_total.field_name = 'total_withheld_taxes'

-- Individual withholdings
JOIN form_categories fc_1099 ON fc_1099.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_withheld_1099 ON ff_withheld_1099.category_id = fc_1099.id
    AND ff_withheld_1099.field_name = 'withheld_tax_from_1099'

JOIN form_categories fc_w2 ON fc_w2.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_withheld_w2 ON ff_withheld_w2.category_id = fc_w2.id
    AND ff_withheld_w2.field_name = 'withheld_tax_from_W2'

JOIN form_categories fc_other ON fc_other.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_withheld_other ON ff_withheld_other.category_id = fc_other.id
    AND ff_withheld_other.field_name = 'withheld_tax_from_other_forms'

-- Join for self-employment tax
JOIN form_categories fc_se ON fc_se.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_self_employment ON ff_self_employment.category_id = fc_se.id
    AND ff_self_employment.field_name = 'other_taxes'

WHERE 
    -- Use one of the following filters:
    c.id = 1ad955cb-1e76-4899-8deb-d04745216ecf                     
    -- OR c.full_name = 'John Doe'   
    -- OR c.email = 'john@example.com' 

ORDER BY f.file_year DESC;

SELECT 
    c.id AS client_id,
    c.full_name,
    c.email,
    f.file_year,

    ff_overpay.field_value AS overpayment_amount,
    ff_estpay.field_value AS estimated_payments

FROM clients c
JOIN files f ON f.client_id = c.id
JOIN forms fo ON fo.file_id = f.id

-- Join for overpayment
JOIN form_categories fc_overpay ON fc_overpay.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_overpay ON ff_overpay.category_id = fc_overpay.id
    AND ff_overpay.field_name = 'overpayment_amount'

-- Join for estimated payments
JOIN form_categories fc_estpay ON fc_estpay.form_id = fo.id
JOIN form_fields ff_estpay ON ff_estpay.category_id = fc_estpay.id
    AND ff_estpay.field_name = 'estimated_payments'

WHERE 
    -- Use one of the following filters:
    c.id = '1ad955cb-1e76-4899-8deb-d04745216ecf'                     
    -- OR c.full_name = 'John Doe'   
    -- OR c.email = 'john@example.com' 

ORDER BY f.file_year DESC;
